===Etymology===
From {{inh|az|trk-pro|*yara||wound}}<ref>{{R:tut-pro:SDM|*dal-g-|url=http://starling.rinet.ru/cgi-bin/response.cgi?single=1&basename=%2fdata%2falt%2fturcet&text_number=384&root=config}}</ref>, from which {{cog|az|yarıq}} with the same meaning is also derived.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|az|[jɑˈrɑ]}}
* {{hyphenation|az|ya|ra}}
===Noun===
